Brooke Kazuko Elby (amụrụ na Mee 24, 1993) bụ onye America bụbu onye na-agba bọọlụ n'etiti / onye na-echebe bụ onye ikpeazụ gbara bọọlụ maka Chicago Red Stars na National Women's Soccer League (NWSL). Ọ bụ onye isi nchịkwa nke abụọ nke NWSL Players Association.
Ọ gbara bọọlụ na Boston Breakers na Melbourne Victory nke Australian W-League
Elby bụ onye otu Boston Breakers mgbe ha kwụsịrị na Jenụwarị, 2018
Ọ bụ Utah Royals FC họpụtara ya na Boston Breakers Dispersal Draft Na June 18, 2018, e rere Elby na Chicago Red Stars. Na Disemba 16, 2019, Elby kwupụtara ezumike nká ya na bọọlụ ọkachamara.
N'afọ 2019, a họpụtara Elby dịka onye isi oche nke National Women's Soccer League Players Association (NWSLPA), na-anọchi Yael Averbuch
Mgbe ọ lara ezumike nká na bọọlụ ọkachamara, Elby weere ọrụ onye isi nchịkwa na NWSLPA. N'ọnwa Eprel 2021, Meghann Burke nọchiri Elby dị ka onye isi nchịkwa NWSLPA.
